defaultHer achievements feature winning the British Universities Cham
defaultpionship with Loughborough, captaining Lichfield from 2005-09, the North East U18 and Northumberland U16 sides. Her international triumphs span the Six Nations five times, together with the European Championship, Nations Cup and European Trophy twice each.
default Personal accolades are players’ player awards at Novocastrians, Lichfield, Loughborough University and the England Academy.
